<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="18Sep1936"><font color="red">18 September 1936</font> <i>NLJL</i> (from Paul L&eacute;on to Messrs Monro Saw): John Lane &hellip; had something like six months for setting up the book &hellip; whereas the Albatross edition set up their edition in six weeks. </div>
